title: Rawsome
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, All Raw
description: Organic raw cafe, opened Aug 2013 at Nieuwstad 9 and move here in 2015. Serves raw food, fresh juices, and raw desserts. Honey is used in a few items. Casual, has Wi-Fi.
venueHours: Mon 12:00pm-7:00pm, Tue-Wed 9:00am-7:00pm, Thu 9:00am-9:00pm, Fri 9:00am-7:00pm, Sat 9:00am-6:00pm, Sun 12:00pm-6:00pm
